{
  "stem": "8569.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "After the revolt, the Germans found these little handmade grenades and they identified the gunpowder, which, of course, we didn't know that gunpowder had some kind of special characteristic.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They identified this gunpowder as coming only from the union and the only from [GERMAN], where my sister worked.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] started an investigation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They imprisoned four girls-- Roza Robota, Ella Gartner, Regina Safirsztain, and Ester Wajcblum.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They tortured them mercilessly and eventually hanged them publicly on January 5, 1945.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] During the period of my sister being incarcerated in the bunker which was a prison within the prison, Marta succeeded to bring me letters from her and from Jakob, who was the kapo of this bunker.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was very, very sympathetic to the girls.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And through him, I received letters-- [BACKGROUND NOISE]",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Marta brought, brought letters.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was trying to get me to see my sister.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it never materialized.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But Marta, sawing my depression, arranged with bribes to put me in a hospital in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At this point, the union commander was in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And as she was trying to reassure me and tell me-- apparently Jakob [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] received an order to execute the girls.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he was stalling for time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he refused.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He had the power to refuse it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he said he's not going to execute all the order and-- unless he's going to get it from Berlin.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So it lasted for a while.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And finally the order from Berlin came, and he didn't have a choice.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Marta was always coming and visiting me every day.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
